'''Battle Tactician''' was a title for a member of the [[warrior caste]] of the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]. Battle Tacticians were usually more strategy-based than the average warrior, and were usually more prone to statistics and assessments with their enhanced brain.<ref name="HT">''[[The New Jedi Order: Agents of Chaos I: Hero's Trial]]''</ref> They also had a much calmer temperament than the average warrior. Battle Tacticians were usually found in the command chambers of war vessels, advising their [[Commander/Legends|Commanders]] of the status of their fleets.

The warrior [[Raff]] and [[Nas Choka's tactician|unnamed Nas Choka's tactician]] served as Battle Tacticians.

